Class LocalDateAndTimeStampImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.impl.BasicNotifierImpl

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LocalDateAndTimeStamp, Triplet, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject

    public class LocalDateAndTimeStampImpl
extends TripletImpl
implements LocalDateAndTimeStamp
    An implementation of the model object 'Local Date And Time Stamp'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Stamp Type
    • THun Year
    • Ten Year
    • Day
    • Hour
    • Minute
    • Second
    • Hund Sec
